title: Urban Beans
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Fusion
description: This vegetarian restaurant, coffee cafe, and wine bar is open 24-hours. Features daily offerings, fresh baked goods, and vegan breakfast and lunch options like quiche, scones, and scramble. Local vegan beer and wine at happy hour. Hosts occasional live music and events. Free Wi-Fi. Est. since 2009.
